attributes.Long form description: The student is replacing the battery and micro SD card in their GoPro, and attaching it to a tripod and handheld grip. They first remove the old battery and insert a new one, then change the micro SD card. Next, they turn on the GoPro, then turn it off and open the mount. They remove a screw from the strap, attach the strap to the GoPro, and screw it on. Finally, they remove the GoPro from the tripod and handheld grip.
